Mick Moloney Irish-American Music and Popular Culture Field Recordings

Concert and Session at Lenape Park, Philadelphia, PA. Musicians include: Mike Preston, Mike Rafferty (flutes), Mick Moloney (banjo), Thomas Standeven (uilleann pipes), John Vesey (fiddle), Gena Dunlop (vocals, bodhran), Joe Mulroney (vocals), Maureen McDade Irish Dancers, Randy Moore (vocals, guitar, banjo), Unidentified Bluegrass and Old Time musicians. (Two CDs – Total length: 01:50:37) aiamm198C, 199C
